{"article_id":"Lsi5QLVby6VRafMV","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"U.S. President Donald Trump offered up a handful of legal arguments in a series of tweets on Thursday","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"distancing himself from former personal attorney Michael Cohen ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"who was sentenced to prison on Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"for arranging 2016 hush-money payments to women","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"who say","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"they had affairs with the married president .","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"Cohen admitted","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"his actions were aimed at influencing the election in violation of campaign finance laws","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"they were directed by Trump .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"But the president said in his tweets","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"he never told Cohen to break the law","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"and that the payments were unrelated to the campaign .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"The early-morning tweets came","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"as the legal pressure on Trump intensified .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"Also on Wednesday , federal prosecutors in New York announced","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"they had reached a cooperation deal with National Enquirer publisher American Media Inc ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"which admitted making a hush payment to a former Playboy model","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"to prevent her from going public with Trump affair allegations before the 2016 election .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Trump has offered a shifting defense on the payments ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"first saying in April","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"he did not know about them .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Later , he seemed to acknowledge","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"the payments were made ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"but said","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"they were unrelated to campaign finances ,","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"as he said again in the latest tweets .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"Cohen ,","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"who once said","depth":14},{"id":30,"text":"he would \" take a bullet for Trump , \"","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"was sentenced in New York to three years in prison","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"for orchestrating the payments in violation of campaign finance laws before the 2016 U.S. presidential election .","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"He called the payments part of the \" dirty deeds \"","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"he did at Trump ' s behest .","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"Federal prosecutors said","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"Trump ordered the payouts","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"to protect his campaign from the allegations of sexual affairs .","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"Trump wrote on Twitter :","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"\" I never directed Michael Cohen to break the law .","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"He was a lawyer","depth":15},{"id":41,"text":"and he is supposed to know the law .","depth":15},{"id":42,"text":"It is called ' advice of counsel. ' ...","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"This was not campaign finance . \"","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"The president continued :","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"\" Cohen was guilty on many charges","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"unrelated to me . \"","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"The main defense","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"Trump and his lawyers have put forth in recent weeks","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"is that the payments were not subject to campaign finance laws","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"because they were aimed at protecting his personal reputation","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"and would have been made","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"even if he had not been a candidate for president .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"His claim on Twitter","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"to have relied on advice of counsel","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"was new though ,","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"but legal experts expressed skepticism","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"it would work .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"Jessica Levinson , a professor of election law at Loyola Law School in Los Angeles , explained","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"that the defense ,","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"often invoked by corporations in complex transactions ,","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"depends on a party","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"relying on lawyers in good faith .","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"But ,","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"if Trump had wanted legal advice on this issue ,","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"he would have sought out specialized campaign finance lawyers rather than Cohen ,","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"Levinson said .","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"Trump ' s campaign did have such specialized counsel , a team of election lawyers from Jones Day","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"led by Don McGahn ,","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"who would go on to serve as White House counsel .","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"Justice Department policy is not to indict a sitting president ,","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"but some legal experts have said","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"Trump could be charged","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"after leaving office .","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"Democrats and other critics also have raised the issue of impeachment by Congress .","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"Trump has denied the affairs .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"He has also denied the main focus of the investigation by Special Counsel Robert Mueller :","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"whether his campaign colluded with Moscow in its meddling in the 2016 campaign .","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"The Kremlin has denied","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"that any meddling occurred .","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"Trump has routinely blasted the Mueller investigation as a \" witch hunt . \"","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"Mueller referred the Cohen prosecution to federal prosecutors in New York earlier this year .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"Prosecutors on Wednesday also said","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"the publisher of the National Enquirer tabloid had struck a deal","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"to avoid charges over its role in one of the payments","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"made \" in concert \" with Trump ' s presidential campaign .","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"Cohen ,","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"who also pleaded to tax evasion and lying to Congress about a proposed Trump Organization building in Moscow ,","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"in court on Wednesday said","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"his \" blind loyalty \" led him to cover up for Trump .","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"Cohen is the latest Trump associate","depth":5},{"id":91,"text":"to be swept up in Mueller ' s investigation","depth":5},{"id":92,"text":"following Trump ' s campaign chairman Paul Manafort , former deputy campaign chairman Rick Gates and former national security adviser Michael Flynn , among others .","depth":4},{"id":93,"text":"In an interview with this week , Trump slammed Cohen for cooperating with prosecutors","depth":4},{"id":94,"text":"and said","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"he was unconcerned about possible impeachment .","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"He also called any of his potential business dealings with Russia \" peanut stuff. \"","depth":5},{"id":97,"text":"[ nL1N1YH067 ]","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":195,"left":0,"right":194,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":194,"left":189,"right":193,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":189,"left":186,"right":188,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":186,"left":112,"right":185,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":110,"right":111,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":103,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":99,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":1,"right":2,"